# Choose a Policy Template

Use this page to decide which starter template to use when creating a new policy. At the moment, the hub has one approved template, but this page gives us a place to add more template options later without changing the rest of the guidance.

---

## Current Template Options

### MoJ Policy Template

Use this for standard Ministry of Justice Digital, Data and Science policies.

- Best for new policies that follow the current hub structure
- Includes the required policy details, governance sections, review cycle, and support contacts
- Recommended starting point for most new policy work

[Open the MoJ Policy Template](policy-template.html)

---

## How to Use This Template

1. Open the template.
2. Copy it into a new policy file.
3. Replace the placeholder text with your policy content.
4. Follow the step-by-step guidance in [Adding a New Policy](adding-a-policy.html).

If we add more approved templates in future, they can be listed on this page alongside the standard option.